-- Bajaj Auto Gains in Mumbai Trading After July Sales Increases to a Record
-- Siddharth Philip
-- 2010-08-02T03:38:48Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-08-02/bajaj-auto-gain-in-mumbai-trading-after-july-sales-increases-to-a-record.html

          
          
             Bajaj Auto Ltd. rose in Mumbai
trading after saying sales of motorcycles and three-wheelers
climbed 65 percent to a record in July.  
 The shares rose as much as 2.3 percent and traded at 2,735
rupees as of 9:06 a.m. local time.  
